023package com.restfb.types.whatsapp.platform.send.interactive;
024
025import java.util.ArrayList;
026import java.util.List;
027import com.restfb.Facebook;
028import com.restfb.types.AbstractFacebookType;
029
030public class Section extends AbstractFacebookType {
031  @Facebook("product_items")
032  private List<Product> productItems;
033  @Facebook
034  private List<Row> rows;
035  @Facebook
036  private String title;
037
038
039  public static class Product extends AbstractFacebookType {
040    @Facebook("product_retailer_id")
041    private String productRetailerId;
042
043    public Product(String productRetailerId) {
044      this.productRetailerId = productRetailerId;
045    }
046  }
047
048
049  public static class Row extends AbstractFacebookType {
050    @Facebook
051    private String id;
052    @Facebook
053    private String title;
054    @Facebook
055    private String description;
056
057    public Row(String id, String title) {
058      this.id = id;
059      this.title = title;
060    }
061
062    @java.lang.SuppressWarnings("all")
063    public void setDescription(final String description) {
064      this.description = description;
065    }
066  }
067
068  public Section addRow(Row row) {
069    if (rows == null) {
070      rows = new ArrayList<>();
071    }
072    rows.add(row);
073    return this;
074  }
075
076  public Section addProductItem(Product product) {
077    if (productItems == null) {
078      productItems = new ArrayList<>();
079    }
080    productItems.add(product);
081    return this;
082  }
083
084  @java.lang.SuppressWarnings("all")
085  public void setTitle(final String title) {
086    this.title = title;
087  }
088}
